snippet.title: Official Game Awards Trailer – Indiana Jones and the Great Circle
snippet.description:
Adventure Calls! Indiana Jones and the Great Circle is available now on Xbox Series X|S, Game Pass, and PC. Play what GamesRadar+ calls “Undoubtedly one of the best, most singular adventures”. 

ESRB RATING: Teen with Violence, Blood and gore, Mild language, Drug reference
